items.text:
Heyyy! I’m Anne Musisi and I’m an actor, director, and career development coach with a mission to help creatives and actors thrive. Drawing on decades of experience in global theatre, screen, and coaching, I’ve created a wellbeing tool designed specifically for actors and creatives. My mission is to help you overcome self-doubt, reconnect with your creative core, and build a sustainable, fulfilling career.

It is also a tool that can be used by therapists, coaches and facilitators to spark deeper conversations and even provide a thematic structure for your workshops. 

My work merges creative practice with personal growth and career strategy. This tool is the practical embodiment of my belief: that when creatives nurture their inner life, their art and profession flourish too.

If you or anyone are interested in learning more, do feel free to DM. I’d love to chat more.
https://www.annemusisi.com

sharedPost.text:
**Poszukiwani statyści do programu TV** 🎥

Do realizacji jednej ze scen programu telewizyjnego poszukujemy:
* **Statystki**
* **Statysty**

Wymagania:
* Zadbana sylwetka i pewność siebie przed kamerą,
* Gotowość do wystąpienia w scenie, w której obecny będzie kostium kąpielowy lub bielizna (estetyczna, nienachalna forma).

Miejsce i termin
* 3 października
* Wrocław

Osoby zainteresowane, zapraszam do kontaktu na priv.

sharedPost.text:
**SERIAL HISTORYCZNY - ŁÓDŹ**

Na plan serialu kryminalnego szukamy statystów dnia 01.10 lub 02.10. **Mogę Państwa zgłaszać na obie daty, ale udział można wziąć tylko w jednym terminie.**

**Szukamy:**
* **Statyści: **kobiety i mężczyźni w wieku 18-70 lat - naturalny wygląd, bez widocznych tatuaży, bez widocznych operacji, panowie ogoleni i bez nowoczesnych fryzur; panie - bez sztucznych rzęs, hybryd na paznokciach itd.
* **Statyści: **dzieci w wieku 10-12 lat.

**Stawka: **120 zł / dorośli; 130 zł / dzieci.

**Gdzie: **Łódź.

**Kiedy: **01.10 lub 02.10 (można wziąć udział w jednym dniu)

*Dojazd we własnym zakresie.

*Prosimy o zgłoszenia z aktualnymi zdjęciami.

**Zgłoszenia **proszę wysyłać na adres: wawa.statysci@gmail.com

podając: imię i nazwisko, wiek, numer kontaktowy, AKTUALNE zdjęcia, **informacja, na którą datę się zgłaszasz.** W tytule: "Łódź, 01.10 i/lub 02.10".

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of 1 person

sharedPost.text:
**🎬 CASTING DO TELEDYSKU – PŁATNE 🎬**

**Warszawa**

Poszukujemy osób z doświadczeniem aktorskim lub modelingowym do udziału w teledysku młodego i bardzo utalentowanego wykonawcy. Projekt ma charakter surrealistyczny i konceptualny.

📅** Termin realizacji: 05.10 (niedziela), godz. 14:00 – ok. 02:00** (część nocy)

💰 **Projekt płatny**

👉** Poszukiwane role:**

**1. Dziadek** – mężczyzna w wieku 50–75 lat

**2. Mężczyzna** – w wieku 30–45 lat

📩 Zgłoszenia prosimy przesyłać na adres: **casting.kamilaboichenko@gmail.com**

W tytule maila należy wpisać: **ROLA – TELEDYSK – Imię i Nazwisko**

**Do zgłoszenia należy dołączyć:**

1. Imię i nazwisko + wiek

2. Miasto zamieszkania

3. Aktualne zdjęcia (portret + sylwetka)

4. Informację o doświadczeniu + wizytówkę lub showreel (jeśli jest)

5. Wymiary, rozmiar ubrań i butów

6. Dane kontaktowe: nr telefonu i adres e-mail

Zapraszam do udziału w wyjątkowym projekcie – czekamy na Wasze zgłoszenia!

Pozdrawiam serdecznie,

Reżyserka castingu 

Kamila Boichenko

Er du en lille pige som altid har ønsket at stå foran et kamera? 

Til kortfilmen “Dukkebarn” søger vi en pige med en ben protese eller arm protese til rollen som AURA. 

Lidt om filmen: 
“Dukkebarn udforsker den skrøbelige grænse mellem fantasi og virkelighed gennem øjnene på Aura. Hendes fascination til dukker bliver en måde at bearbejde hendes egen smertelige virkelighed og hendes forhold til sin krop. Gennem leg, skabelse og destruktion konfronteres hun med sine dybeste frugter og længsler. 

Alder: I mellem 6-12 år. 

Vi filmer i Århus d. 16-18 Januar 2026. Jobbet vil være lønnet, samt forplejning og transport. Søg gerne lige meget hvor i landet du bor. Vi ser gerne så mange som muligt;) 

Skriv til @Rirh.prod@gmail.com med emnet “CASTING -DUKKEBARN”. Skrive gerne lidt om dig selv, samt er billede og evt erfaring. 

Hvis du er gået videre til casting, eller fået rollen vil du få svar inden 10 Januar. 

Jeg glæder mig til at høre fra jer. 

Mvh Rebecca Renner Hansen - Dukkebarn film

items.text:
**UKRYTA PRAWDA  - WARSZAWA (20-22.10)**

Poszukuję epizodystów do ról:
1. **DOMINIKA  (22-26 lat)** -  studentka marketingu,  bardzo atrakcyjna, zadbana*. 20-22.10 Stawka 1800 zł KONIECZNE DOŚWIADCZENIE/DEMO*
2. **MAKS (7-10 lat)*** - *drobny, rezolutny, poważny jak na swój wiek. Ma astmę. Stawka 800 zł, 2 dni 
3. **PATRYCJA (22-26 lat)*** - *pracuje w korporacji, ubrana w stylu smart casual. Sympatyczna, serdeczna, stawka 700 zł, 5 scen, 2 dni 
4. **MAŁGORZATA (38-45 lat) **- ubrana skromnie, szara kobieta, ale bardzo surowa i przemocowa wobec dzieci.*, 350 zł, 2 sceny, 1 dzień*
5. **ALEKS (47-55 lat) **- ubrany w stylu smart casual. Uprzejmy, taktowny*. stawka 300 zł, 1 scena, 1 dzień *

EPIZODY:
* **Pani Komisarz (44-48 lat)** – w cywilu, czarny garnitur, kilka zdań, Stawka 200 zł 
* **Aspirant (27-33 lata) ** - policjant po cywilu, stawka 200 zł 

📩 Mailowo proszę przesłać informacje: imię i nazwisko, wiek, wzrost, numer telefonu oraz materiały: wideo wizytówkę, aktualne zdjęcia i informacje o doświadczeniu. Wybrane osoby zostaną poproszone o nagranie 1 sceny. 

Zgłoszenia kierujemy na: [patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl](mailto:patrycja.lewandowska@constantin-entertainment.pl) w tytule wpisując nazwę roli.

**SERIAL HISTORYCZNY - ŁÓDŹ - 04.10**

Na plan serialu kryminalnego szukamy statystów oraz **epizodysty do roli z tekstem** na plan 04.10:
* **Statyści i epizodysta: **mężczyźni w wieku ok. 30-50 lat - naturalny wygląd, bez widocznych tatuaży, ogoleni i bez nowoczesnych fryzur; rozmiar max. L, 170-180 cm wzrostu.

**Statysta: 120 zł.**
**Epizodysta: 350 zł.**

**Gdzie: **Łódź.

**Kiedy: **04.10.

*Dojazd we własnym zakresie.

*Prosimy o zgłoszenia z aktualnymi zdjęciami.

**Zgłoszenia **proszę wysyłać na adres: wawa.statysci@gmail.com

podając: imię i nazwisko, wiek, numer kontaktowy, AKTUALNE zdjęcia, a w przypadku epizodystów - dodatkowo wizytówka.

Proszę podać informację**, czy zgłaszasz się na statystowanie, epizod czy na jedno i drugie.** W tytule: "Łódź - 04.10".

items.text: Hello everyone! My name is Hannah Benavides and I am a junior radio, television, and film student at the University of Texas at Austin. I am taking an advanced narrative production class this semester and my script was picked to turn into a short film! If you know anyone that would be interested in auditioning for one of the roles listed, comment down below or message me! You can audition from anywhere in Texas. You do not have to be from Austin. If you have questions feel free to ask. Thank you!!

💀✨ Ladies  ✨💀
Why settle for the same old dinner and drinks when you could share goosebumps, laughter, and unforgettable memories under the glow of the lanterns?

Columbia's Haunted Lantern Tour is the ultimate Girls’ Night Out — a mix of chills, history, and stories that will have you holding each other’s arms (and maybe screaming just a little 👻).

📞 Call 717-587-5368 to reserve your spots and make this year’s girls’ night one to remember… because nothing bonds friends quite like walking through a cemetery after dark.

Warszawa! Na plan serialu Gliniarze poszukujemy epizodystów: 
        1. Anna Jodłowicz (31) – bardzo atrakcyjna kobieta, dobrze ubrana, ambitna asystentka Prezesa, szczerze w nim zakochana, liczy że odejdzie od Żony i zostaną parą. 2 sceny - jedno zdanie, scena wymagająca emocjonalnie 

Data: 09.października
Stawka: 250 zł netto
 

Chętne osoby zapraszam do wysyłania zgłoszeń na adres: casting.outset@interia.pl

W tytule maila proszę o wpisanie nazwy postaci
W treści:
Wiek/wzrost/waga
Info o dotychczasowym doświadczeniu
Linki do swoich materiałów video - wizytówka/demo/scenki ze swoim udziałem

Nie zwracamy kosztów dojazdu i noclegu

CASTING CALL: FOSSILIZED - A CU DENVER STUNDENT FILM  

We are desperately looking for child actors for Fossilized, a senior thesis student film in the CU Denver FiTV program. This is unpaid, and will instead be a copy/credit/meal basis.

If interested, please reach out to -

Rowan Harper (Casting Director) at rowan.harper@ucdenver.edu

Arthur Rice (Producer) at arthur.rice@ucdenver.edu

Can you make a film in 72 hours?  Register today for Season 6! You don’t have to live in Colorado to participate. Just follow our time zones. Make sure to like and follow our page to keep up to date with the upcoming networking events. 

www.kickassfilmfest.com

sharedPost.text:
Kickass Filmmakers! It’s go time! Registration is now officially open for the 6th Annual 72-Hour Kickass Film Fest!

Think you have what it takes to write, shoot, and edit a short film in just 72 hours? We’re challenging you to push your creativity to the limit. Every team will be assigned a random genre, plus a line of dialogue, prop, and character that must be in your 5-7 minute film.

You don’t have to live in Colorado to compete, but you’ll need to follow our time zone.

And the best part? After the challenge, you’ll get to celebrate your hard work at a red-carpet premiere and awards night with over 300 filmmakers and film lovers!

This is just the beginning. We have so many exciting announcements in store for Season 6. Are you up for the challenge? Can you make a film in 72 hours? Register today!  Link in bio!

Sziasztok ! :) 

🍂* A nagy érdeklődésre való tekintettel ismét toborzást tartunk statiszta és hostess pozícióink betöltésére*. 🍂

🎃Kifejezetten a pörgős őszi időszakra keresünk még **8-10 főt **a csapatunk bővítése céljából hetente végezhető alkalmi munkáinkra. 🎃

A betöltésre váró pozíciók: 
-** Közönség statiszta Tv műsorokba** 📺
- **Háttér szereplés reklámokban, filmekben és TV műsorokban **🎞
- **Kiemelt statiszta munka** 🎬
- **Kisebb szereplő munka** 🎤
- **Rendezvény hostess** 🎈
- **Promóciós hostess** 🛍

A bérek : 
- statiszta munkáknál **5.000-60.000** Ft között mozognak / nap 💰
- hostess munkáknál **2.000-2.500** Ft között mozognak / óra  💸

A munkavégzés helyszíne: 
**Bp. - Pest megye **, ezért fővárosi jelentkezőket tudok fogadni📍

A munkavállalás rugalmas, nincs kötelező óraszám amit teljesíteni kellene. Hétköznap és hétvégén egyaránt. 🥳🤩

***Jelentkezni üzenetben vagy kommenten tudtok akár párban is baráttal/barátnővel/testvérrel.. stb. ***📩

** CASTING-AUFRUF – UGC-Videodreh für Immobilienprojekt in Hamburg // 30.09.2025**

 **Drehort:** Hamburg 

 **Drehtag:** Dienstag, 30. September 2025 – Start: 10:00 Uhr

 **Dauer:** ca. 4–5 Stunden (halber Drehtag)

 **Honorar:** 500 € Pauschalgage
** Was wir drehen:**

Die Clips bestehen aus **authentischen Monologen**, die direkt in die Kamera gesprochen werden: **klar, sympathisch, ruhig und professionell**.
* Skriptlänge: 40–60 Sekunden pro Clip
* Teleprompter ist vor Ort (kein Auswendiglernen nötig)
* Fokus: **seriöse, glaubwürdige Darstellung**
** Wen wir suchen:**

* Alter: 25–35 Jahre
* Look: gepflegt, urban, authentisch-professionell (z. B. „Young Professional“-Vibe – denkbar wären Start-up-Gründer, Immobilienberater, Creator mit Vertrauensausstrahlung)
* Sprache: Hochdeutsch, **klare Artikulation** und sichere Präsenz vor der Kamera
* Erfahrung mit Social Media Ads ist ein Plus, aber **keine Voraussetzung**

Unser Schwerpunkt: **Marketingkampagnen für Immobilienvertriebe, Bauträger und Kapitalanlagen im gesamten DACH-Raum**.

* Styling-Hinweise & Text-Input durch uns (kein Kostüm notwendig, clean/professionell reicht)

𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦 𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐬𝐞𝐥𝐟 𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐨 𝐍𝐨𝐭 𝐉𝐮𝐬𝐭 𝐚 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐟𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐚𝐥 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐫, 𝐁𝐮𝐭 𝐚𝐧 𝐔𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐩𝐩𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐅𝐨𝐫𝐜𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐀𝐜𝐚𝐝𝐞𝐦𝐲!

** **

Whether you're just starting or want to improve the talent you already have, Marble Academy in Swinton, Manchester, will help unlock your full potential and refine your craft to help capture the attention of casting directors in film, television, and theatre.

 

Here’s why you should seize this incredible opportunity:

**Renowned Excellence**: Marble Academy is not only celebrated by Spotlight as one of the premier drama academies in the country, but is also the recipient of the 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫 & 𝐍𝐨𝐫𝐭𝐡 𝐖𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐠𝐞 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐓𝐡𝐞𝐚𝐭𝐫𝐞 𝐒𝐜𝐡𝐨𝐨𝐥 𝐎𝐟 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐘𝐞𝐚𝐫.
Here, you won’t just learn; you’ll train with one of the best in the business!

 

**Authentic Training**: Our L.A.M.D.A.-qualified tutor, Christian Le Feuvre, brings a wealth of real-world experience that empowers you to delve deeply into characters and scenes. His insightful feedback doesn’t just boost your confidence; it ignites your growth as an actor, providing you with a fresh perspective on every script. With his nurturing and constructive coaching style, you’ll be amazed at how he can transform your journey as an actor.

 

But don’t just take our word for it—explore the glowing reviews and dive into our programme details for a closer look at what we offer at www.marbleacademy.co.uk

 

Audition dates are still available!

 

Don’t let this incredible opportunity pass you by—take the first step towards a world of extraordinary possibilities in your acting career—email [marbleacademy@hotmail.com](mailto:marbleacademy@hotmail.com) for more information and to book your audition slot.

Casting!

​[Gdańsk]

Szukam tancerki (tancerki/aktorki) do spektaklu Lilije; to mroczny i epicki spektakl dramatyczno-taneczny na podstawie ballady Mickiewicza z tańcem, grą na instrumentach i śpiewem wieloglosowym na żywo.

Tu zwiastun: [https://youtube.com/shorts/QoVYI9z-c0E?si=vL0OseuQpHg_DtLT](https://youtube.com/shorts/QoVYI9z-c0E?si=vL0OseuQpHg_DtLT)

Tu więcej informacji: [https://www.facebook.com/share/18bUFBgxwr/](https://www.facebook.com/share/18bUFBgxwr/)

Rola zasadniczo bez te​kstu; kilka linijek mówionych wspólnie ze wszystkimi. Umiejętność śpiewu, szczególnie na biało, będzie dużym atutem. Taniec współczesny, improwizacja, teatr tańca są wymagane.

Projekt non-profit, próby w październiku i listopadzie w poniedziałki od 19:30-21:30 w ACK UG. Spektakle płatne, w tym roku grania 7 i 14 grudnia. 

Premiera odbyła się w czerwcu, spektakl cieszył się dużym zainteresowaniem.

Zgłoszenie prześlij na [weronikakamola@gmail.com](mailto:weronikakamola@gmail.com), a w nim:

- ​zdjęcie, wzrost i wiek

- opis swojego doświadczenia tanecznego i śpiewaczego 

- filmik, na którym widać, jak tańczysz

items.text:
**WARSZAWA **

**4, 6 i 7 października**

**6 i 7 października (ŁÓDŹ - transport w obie strony)**

film fabularny

Zapraszamy Was na plan kolejnego filmu. Tym razem "JAN BO" czyli film biograficzny o Janku Borysewiczu. 

Szukamy Statystów w wieku ok. 17-30 lat, którzy będą chcieli pobawić się z nami przez te 3 dni na scenach koncertu.

Ponieważ gramy lata 80te mamy nieuniknione wytyczne charakteryzacji:

**Dla wszystkich:**
* brak tatuaży w widocznych miejscach (ręce również, na nogach u pań też odpadają)
* bez tuneli w uszach
* kolczyki w nosie, brwiach czy wardze trzeba wyjąć na zdjęcia

**Panowie:**
* bez wygolonych boków i bez włosów ścinanych maszynką, bez zarostów od barbera
* długie włosy super
* łysi panowie niestety odpadają

**Panie:**
* paznokcie najlepiej naturalne. Jeśli hybryda, musi być pomalowana na zdjęcia na jednolity kolor
* bez permanentnych makijaży, doklejonych rzęs i innych ingerencji współczesnych kosmetologii

**TRANSPORT DLA STATYSTÓW Z ŁODZI 6 i 7 października**

Stawka: 120 zł dla Statystów na 1 dzień

Stawka: 140 zł dla Statystów na 2 lub 3 dni i dla Statystów z Łodzi

Przymiarki stacjonarne w Warszawie na Chełmskiej: 3.10, od 9:00-18:00 godzina do wyboru - płatne dodatkowo 60 zł

Przymiarki online - tylko dla Statystów z Łodzi (wysłanie 3 zdjęć w 3 stylizacjach) - płatne dodatkowo 30 zł

**ZGŁOSZENIA**

Poproszę na adres: **ewelina.wika@podtytulem.pl**

W tytule: **JB + wybrane daty**

W treści: imię i nazwisko, wiek, nr telefonu, miejscowość + wymiary: wzrost, klatka, pas, biodra, rozmiar ubrania i buta

W załączniku: ZDJĘCIE TWARZY I SYLWETKI: tylko z dnia zgłoszenia.

Portretowe selfie w dziennym świetle, na wprost, patrząc w obiektyw. Bez żadnych filtrów. Bez okularów. Bez nakrycia głowy.

Panie - bez makijażu, w rozpuszczonych włosach tak, żeby widoczna była długość włosów

Panowie - dodatkowo zdjęcie z profilu

items.text:
Casting Call

We are looking for actors to make an example scene for the film pitch, with which we are looking for to ask for funding for the feature length low-budget independent film based on a real story, hidden truths and mystic experiences, mixed with fantasy.

The action of the example scene develops, as a guy (20-26 years old) confronts with two young men (26-35 years old), who ask him to give back them money, that a young man borrowed from them for the business, that failed. They are warning him with death and preparing to hit him until death, but accidentally something happens as a hand of help.

It's going be around 3h of filming for one day: 14th of October day time in Croydon, London, next to Waddon station. 

Salary will be £25 for the actor after filming, plus if actor will agree to act in the next, but real film shootings, then agreed compensation of percent of how much the film will earn after distribution.

Acting experience is not necessary, but preferable and being comfortable in front of camera with a wish to act.

Actors:
A young guy with blonde colour hair (20-26 years old)

A young man number 1 with black or brown hair  (26-35 years old)

A young man number 2 with black or brown hair (26-35 years old)

If you are interested, write me:

I am producer and one of the directors of the film. My name: Ieva Kondrataviciute 
Email: ieva.kristina.kondrataviciute@gmail.com
Contact WhatsApp: +44 7548710376

items.text:
INTENSE CRIME DRAMA - SHORT (PAID)

1-day shoot in London (UK) for 1st week in November 2025 (date tbc)

Summary: Set in the backroom of a dive bar. A night of heavy drinking ends in a deadly contest between newfound besties - a fearless Nigerian gangland enforcer and a trigger-happy European gunman.

MALE LEAD: to play fearless gangland enforcer. Black African, 25-35, Nigerian accent, 5’6”+, athletic physique with good fitness and conditioning. Stage combat training. Flat rate of £500 for 20 hours (rehearsals & shoot).

MALE LEAD: to play trigger-happy gunman. White European, 25-35, 5’ 6”+, 85kg-100kg, powerful physique with good fitness and conditioning. Stage combat training. Flat rate of £300 for 15 hours.

You will need professional experience playing roles on Stage, Film or TV. Please send in a cover letter, your CV with headshot and your showreel to Davina Brown at k2filmworks@gmail.com

items.text:
Banbury, Oxfordshire | £250 for 2 days + travel considered

We’re casting for the final scenes of Failsafe, a psychological short film currently in production with a professional crew.

Directed by Rob Hutt — award-winning filmmaker of Time Spent (23 awards, 22 nominations, 8.8 IMDb rating). You can view Rob’s IMDb profile here:

👉 https://lnkd.in/e2u7vA-P

This project is already generating festival momentum and will be featured in Pro Movie Maker Magazine.

ROLE:

 • Female, playing age 25–35

 • Character: A game designer whose reality begins to fracture, blurring with the world she created. Performance requires range: strength, vulnerability, psychological depth.

DETAILS:

 • £250 for 2 days filming.

 • Shoot will take place across one Saturday & Sunday, back-to-back.

 • Filming must be completed on one of the following weekends:

 • 11–12 October 2025

 • 18–19 October 2025

 • 25–26 October 2025

 • Location: Banbury, Oxfordshire. Reasonable travel costs considered.

 • Short film — to be submitted to national and international film festivals.

 • Professional set with full crew.

 • Self-tape auditions required.

📩 To apply / receive the self-tape brief:

Email robhuttfilms@gmail.com or DM directly.

✨ This is a chance to be part of a powerful, festival-ready film with proven pedigree.

CASTING CALL - FEATURE FILM 

Please, do NOT email if you do not fit the brief!

Shooting Location: The Netherlands
Bruce male | 30 – 45 | English: native 
Black, African American or Caribbean

Requirements:
Based in Europe (EU passport)
Native speaker of American English
Age range: 30–45 years old

European based American-English speaking actor for the role of BRUCE in the Dutch Comedy Film.

We are looking for an actor to play the role of young and ambitious American movie director Bruce in the upcoming Dutch comedy film.

The film is based on the best-selling novel Wen Er Maar Aan, written by Dutch actress and author Maike Meijer.

Shooting date: December 3th 2025 in the Netherlands 
Travel day: December 2th 2025 (Travel day back on the same day as the shooting day or the morning after)

Fee:
€4.000 all-in (shooting day + travel day(s))
Overnight stay will be covered by the production
Travel expenses will be covered by the production

If you are selected to record a self-tape, you will receive further details via email.

>> ancagency_submissions@hotmail.com

items.summary:
CASTING CALL - FEATURE FILM 

Please, do NOT email if you do not fit the brief!

Shooting Location: The Netherlands
Bruce male | 30 – 45 | English: native 
Black, African American or Caribbean

Requirements:
Based in Europe (EU passport)
Native speaker of American English
Age range: 30–45 years old

European based American-English speaking actor for the role of BRUCE in the Dutch Comedy Film.

We are looking for an actor to play the role of young and ambitious American movie director Bruce in the upcoming Dutch comedy film.

The film is based on the best-selling novel Wen Er Maar Aan, written by Dutch actress and author Maike Meijer.

Shooting date: December 3th 2025 in the Netherlands 
Travel day: December 2th 2025 (Travel day back on the same day as the shooting day or the morning after)

Fee:
€4.000 all-in (shooting day + travel day(s))
Overnight stay will be covered by the production
Travel expenses will be covered by the production

If you are selected to record a self-tape, you will receive further details via email.

>> ancagency_submissions@hotmail.com

The Brookside Theatre, Romford is urgently looking for a male actor (playing age 45-60) for their Halloween production; THE ADDAMS FAMILY 

Role: Mal Beineke (Actor with good comic timing. Does need to sing a few lines but these are character vocals)
Accent: US (General or NYC)

Sadly due to an injury and subsequent surgery, the actor playing role has had to withdraw

Rehearsals: Weekday evenings and Sunday daytimes (some flexibility)

Show dates: 29th Oct - 2nd Nov 2025

Venue: Brookside Theatre, Romford (2 mins walk from Elizabeth Line Station / Free Parking)

Unpaid charity production

If you think you can step in and save the show then please get in touch asap - email casting@brooksidetheatre.com or PM me

Keeping everything crossed as we really don't want to cancel

items.text:
UK Business Owners – We Want You! (Paid Opportunity) PLEASE KINDLY SHARE 🙏🏼

Casper Black Casting is on the lookout for fun, engaging business owners based in or around London for a paid filming opportunity with Quickbooks.

This is your chance to promote your business, appear on a well-known YouTube channel, and take part in some light-hearted, game show-style filming.

🕒 Filming will take place Friday 3rd October in London and will last around 2–3 hours.
💰 Yes, it’s paid.
🎥 Yes, it’s fun.
📣 And yes, it’s a great chance to showcase your personality and your business.

We’re looking for captivating characters who love to share what they do and aren’t afraid to have a bit of fun on camera.

Know someone? Or fancy it yourself? Get in touch now — we’d love to hear from you.

Email casper@casperblackcasting.com with a short paragraph about you and your business.

items.text:
**PROJECT NAME**: *DESTINATION OSHAWA*

**PROJECT TYPE:** *WEBSERIES - COMEDY*

**STATUS:*** NON-UNION*

**COMPENSATION**: DAILY HONORARIUM *CAD $2*00/Day- please note cast and crew for this project are working on an equity daily honorarium. 

**SYPNOPSIS**:  [Hannah is suddenly appointed director of the Oshawa Tourism Board due to her boss’s unexpected passing. She is tasked with getting Oshawa off the “Worst Cities in Canada” list by the end of the year. With almost no resources or time, it’s up to Hannah to inspire her chaotic team and fulfill her promise of putting Oshawa on the map (in a good way).](https://www.canva.com/design/DAGYFsS-yL4/PVPHv0y53k9FrFZNwakJOg/view?utm_content=DAGYFsS-yL4&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=editor#page-1)

***SHOOTING LOCATIONS:**** Richmond Hill + Oshawa*

***PRODUCTION DATES: ****October 17-24 (individual shoot dates TBD)*

***CASTING SUBMISSION INSTRUCTIONS: ***

*To request an audition and sides, please send headshots, reels and any info to **[casting@combobravo.com](mailto:casting@combobravo.com)** with the character name in the subject line. ****ie - BELLA RANDAZZO - ASHLEY***

***CHARACTER****:  *Ashley
***Role Type****: *Lead

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ****33*

***Episode: ****1-4*

***Appearance: ****Brown Hair, sweet face. *Neat, tidy, formal wear in the office. Patagonia vests, khakis on field trips. *Think Gabe Lewis (The Office)*

***About Character:**** *Liaison to City Council, Ashley has always been passionate about efficient government bureaucracy to a fault. His do-gooder nature has always made him generally unlikeable by his peers and higher ups. In high school he was the first class president to be impeached by faculty, and he was the first student to ever be assassinated at model UN. Despite that he never lost his innocence, and kept on pursuing his dream of joining the Canadian government. He loves his job as Council Liaison and self-appointed apprentice to Bill Tuft. He planned his life out long ago and it is going exactly according to plan, until he met Hannah. He fell in love with her as soon as she started working as Bill’s assistant, and when he was drafted to join the Tourism Task Force, he dedicated himself to making sure her goals are achieved. She is truly the one person in his life that throws his rational, ordered nature into disarray. 

***CHARACTER****:  *Sarah

***Role Type****: *Lead

***Presenting Gender: ***Woman

***Age: ****20*

***Episode: ****1-4*

***Appearance: ****5’2, petite, unassuming student. *

***About Character:**** *Newest intern at Oshawa City Hall. Was reassigned to the Tourism Task Force. In a constant state of panic. She wants to please everyone all the time but is constantly second guessing herself. She is very introverted unless she’s having one of her stress- induced, fugue-state outbursts. Fearing for the other students safety, Sarah was sent to Oshawa City Hall by her guidance counsellor as they felt a “noncompetitive and ineffectual environment” would be a good change of pace for her. The task force team is unfazed by her outbursts and for the first time Sarah feels as though she’s found her pack. Their acceptance helps Sarah gain confidence and start standing up for herself.

***CHARACTER****:  *Deborah

***Role Type****: *Lead

***Presenting Gender: ***Woman

***Age: ****60*

***Episode: ****1-4*

***Appearance: ***Stocky, older, greying a bit but also dyes her hair. Business casual, but stopped updating her wardrobe in the 90s.

***About Character:**** *Has been working at City Hall since gaining her business degree from Durham College. She stopped caring about her job around the time everything moved online and although she would never admit it, feels a bit archaic and forgotten. She’s annoyed she was moved onto Hannah’s task force as she doesn't want to waste her time learning new skills for a project that seems destined to fail. She’s not bitter, she's just seen it all before. Eventually, Deborah is motivated after some emotional vulnerability from Hannah, perhaps remembering a younger version of herself.

***CHARACTER****:  *Bill Tuft

***Role Type****: *Reoccuring

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ****51*

***Episode: ****1-2, 4*

***Appearance: ***Tall, athletic, greying. Suit with no tie kind of guy, but always a flashy pocket square. On fridays and weekends he wears his golf attire. Think Richard Greenwood, (Workin’ Moms)

***About Character:**** *Former real estate agent, but has been the Ward 5 City Councillor 15 years running. Bill is considered a “Greybeard” or municipal government. He’s been at it for a long time and knows all the ins and outs. He’s incredibly popular, not just because of his extreme charisma, but also his moral flexibility when it comes allowing a “healthy dose” of political corruption. He likes ambitious people that know what they want, and won’t let moral or legal guidelines stifle their vision. He saw a lot of potential in Hannah when she started as his assistant. When Hannah hit her rock bottom, it was his idea to give her a leave of absence, as he felt a sense of responsibility for her. He’s given Hannah six months to show what she’s made of. If it works, he looks like a genius. If she fails, it’s not much money, his conscience is clear and in the meantime he can use the Task Force to his own personal and financial benefit when the opportunity arises.

***CHARACTER****:  *Nick

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ***28

***Episode: ****2*

***Appearance: ***White, thin and kind of scrawny. Slim shady like. Oshawa generals jersey. Knock off designer hat and shoes. Chain. Energetic, passionate, feels his emotions and is confident in them, which can make him a prima donna. The fashion of J Roc, the delivery of Western U frat bro, and the sincerity of a “cool” youth pastor, 

***About Character:**** *After getting his Bachelors from Western, Nick gave up on higher education to pursue his dream of becoming a hip hop legend. He moved back in with his mom and  new husband, Bill Tuft, at his mansion. That was 5 years ago. When Bill learns that the Task Force is putting together a tourism music video, he sees this as an opportunity to include Nick in order to write off past studio personal expenses. Nick joins forces with Jam Easy in making a great song, and wins his step-dad’s respect of his art. 

***CHARACTER****:  *Gord “Conspiracy Guy” 

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ***39

***Episode: ****2,4*

***Appearance: ***White, grisled beard, weary eyes, military surplus gear, phone mounted on a chest rig. Husky, but strong with a surprising range of movement, like a former soldier who’s stopped training.

***About Character:**** *Gord is a conspiracy-minded “truth warrior” who proudly identifies as a sovereign citizen.  He spends his days moderating threads on Truth Social, and uploading videos of his “auditing” police and other government workers to his pro-freedom channel. He’s paranoid, he’s ready for a fight, but when you get down to it he’s very thin-skinned. He comes across the Oshawa Tourism Task Force filming different Oshawa landmarks, he confronts them for “invading his privacy” and casts paranoid suspicions about their true intent. When Ashley arrives with his ”spy drone”, Gord takes it as a moment of bittersweet triumph: the government really is after him, and his “truth warrior” life wasn’t wasted.

***CHARACTER****:  *Samuel McLaughlin Impersonator #1

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ***45

***Episode: ***3

***Appearance: ***Middle aged man who is neither physically matching nor dressed for the part of Samuel.

***About Character:**** *Samuel shows up to audition as an R.S. McLaughlin impersonator for the upcoming civic holiday, but quickly fails when he not only cannot remember his line - “Oshawa”, but is legally required to let the task force know he’s not allowed within a certain distance of any children at the celebration.  

***CHARACTER****:  *Samuel McLaughlin, R.S

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ***45

***Episode: ***3

***Appearance: ***Teddy Roosevelt aesthetic. Neatly trimmed, but bushy moustache. Balding, broad shoulders, stern, sharp eyes. (Think the real Samuel McLaughlin)

***About Character:**** *Samuel shows up at the office to audition as an R.S. McLaughlin impersonator for the upcoming civic holiday, but he insists he is not an actor at all and seems to believe he’s the real Samuel McLaughlin. Once hired, Samuel lingers in the office and gradually assumes control of the task force by exploiting weaknesses in Hannah’s communication with her team.

***CHARACTER****:  *Willie

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ***66

***Episode: ***4

***Appearance: ***Thinning white/grey uncombed hair, beer belly, red face, weathered skin. Slow moving and a slow vocal pace. He never wants to finish his sentence because it’ll give the listener a chance to leave. Vintage, worn rumpled clothes. A hat that looks like he’s been wearing it for 50 years. 

***About Character:**** *A local Oshawa “Shwallywood legend” that has had hundreds of TV and Movie productions use his driveway. A lonely drinker and compulsive liar, a bad one at that, When Jam Easy needs to stall on his Hollywood Tour, he brings his group to Willie, who shares “Forrest Gumpian” stories of how he changed movie history, and bragging about absurdly close friendships with movie stars. Obviously no one believes him, which makes him sad. He just just excited to have someone to talk to.

***CHARACTER****:*  Clara “Newswoman”

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Woman

***Age: ***40’s

***Episode: ***4

***Appearance: ***Mid-40s, attractive but not delicate, with a confident, professional presence. Simple hair, and a face showing experience rather than youth. Blazer, smart blouse, tailored slacks. Carries a small microphone with the channel logo, Minimal jewelry. 

***About Character: ***Field reporter for a Durham Region news channel. Polished but practical, someone who can run to a chaotic scene without ruining her outfit. Clara is on-site at the Oshawa tourism task force’s Hollywood Tour location, where a body has been discovered. She delivers the story with gravity despite the absurdity of the situation. 

***CHARACTER****:* Chris

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ***29

***Episode: ***4

***Appearance: ***Medium build, white, dark hair. Nerdy, glasses, thrifted clothes or ones he picked up at Costco

***About Character: ***full-time software engineer but would rather talk about his many hobbies and interests like the golden age of cinema, Napoleon, his tropical fish tank, pickleball league and making his girlfriend Julia happy. Chris saw an online ad for the Shwallywood Tour and immediately booked it as he had been looking for a way to propose to his girlfriend, Julia, for months. On the day of, Chris does not immediately react when the tour seems to be taking much longer than anticipated to get to Parkwood as he is a calm and patient person. He only becomes upset when he sees his girlfriend Julia is disappointed in the lackluster activities of the day.

***CHARACTER****:*  Julia

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Woman

***Age: ***29

***Episode: ***4

***Appearance: ***Thin frame, blonde or dark brown hair, A little nerdy, soft goth. 

***About Character: ***Works as a dental assistant. She realized she had a passion for teeth when she did a work placement as a mortician in high school. Julia has been taken on the Shwallywood tour by Chris, to celebrate their anniversary. She initially had very little interest, but Chris insisted on bringing her because she’s a movie buff. The tour is off to a rough start, but as the tour progresses, Julia’s eccentric side emerges. She enjoys the macabre and is intrigued by some of the stranger stops, though her frustration continues as Chris struggles to give an honest take on the experience.

**PROJECT NAME**: *DESTINATION OSHAWA*

**PROJECT TYPE:** *WEBSERIES - COMEDY*

**STATUS:*** NON-UNION*

**COMPENSATION**: DAILY HONORARIUM *CAD $2*00/Day- please note cast and crew for this project are working on an equity daily honorarium. 

**SYPNOPSIS**:  [Hannah is suddenly appointed director of the Oshawa Tourism Board due to her boss’s unexpected passing. She is tasked with getting Oshawa off the “Worst Cities in Canada” list by the end of the year. With almost no resources or time, it’s up to Hannah to inspire her chaotic team and fulfill her promise of putting Oshawa on the map (in a good way).](https://www.canva.com/design/DAGYFsS-yL4/PVPHv0y53k9FrFZNwakJOg/view?utm_content=DAGYFsS-yL4&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link&utm_source=editor#page-1)

***SHOOTING LOCATIONS:**** Richmond Hill + Oshawa*

***PRODUCTION DATES: ****October 17-24 (individual shoot dates TBD)*

***CASTING SUBMISSION INSTRUCTIONS: ***

*To request an audition and sides, please send headshots, reels and any info to **[casting@combobravo.com](mailto:casting@combobravo.com)** with the character name in the subject line. ****ie - BELLA RANDAZZO - ASHLEY***

***CHARACTER****:  *Ashley
***Role Type****: *Lead

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ****33*

***Episode: ****1-4*

***Appearance: ****Brown Hair, sweet face. *Neat, tidy, formal wear in the office. Patagonia vests, khakis on field trips. *Think Gabe Lewis (The Office)*

***About Character:**** *Liaison to City Council, Ashley has always been passionate about efficient government bureaucracy to a fault. His do-gooder nature has always made him generally unlikeable by his peers and higher ups. In high school he was the first class president to be impeached by faculty, and he was the first student to ever be assassinated at model UN. Despite that he never lost his innocence, and kept on pursuing his dream of joining the Canadian government. He loves his job as Council Liaison and self-appointed apprentice to Bill Tuft. He planned his life out long ago and it is going exactly according to plan, until he met Hannah. He fell in love with her as soon as she started working as Bill’s assistant, and when he was drafted to join the Tourism Task Force, he dedicated himself to making sure her goals are achieved. She is truly the one person in his life that throws his rational, ordered nature into disarray. 

***CHARACTER****:  *Sarah

***Role Type****: *Lead

***Presenting Gender: ***Woman

***Age: ****20*

***Episode: ****1-4*

***Appearance: ****5’2, petite, unassuming student. *

***About Character:**** *Newest intern at Oshawa City Hall. Was reassigned to the Tourism Task Force. In a constant state of panic. She wants to please everyone all the time but is constantly second guessing herself. She is very introverted unless she’s having one of her stress- induced, fugue-state outbursts. Fearing for the other students safety, Sarah was sent to Oshawa City Hall by her guidance counsellor as they felt a “noncompetitive and ineffectual environment” would be a good change of pace for her. The task force team is unfazed by her outbursts and for the first time Sarah feels as though she’s found her pack. Their acceptance helps Sarah gain confidence and start standing up for herself.

***CHARACTER****:  *Deborah

***Role Type****: *Lead

***Presenting Gender: ***Woman

***Age: ****60*

***Episode: ****1-4*

***Appearance: ***Stocky, older, greying a bit but also dyes her hair. Business casual, but stopped updating her wardrobe in the 90s.

***About Character:**** *Has been working at City Hall since gaining her business degree from Durham College. She stopped caring about her job around the time everything moved online and although she would never admit it, feels a bit archaic and forgotten. She’s annoyed she was moved onto Hannah’s task force as she doesn't want to waste her time learning new skills for a project that seems destined to fail. She’s not bitter, she's just seen it all before. Eventually, Deborah is motivated after some emotional vulnerability from Hannah, perhaps remembering a younger version of herself.

***CHARACTER****:  *Bill Tuft

***Role Type****: *Reoccuring

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ****51*

***Episode: ****1-2, 4*

***Appearance: ***Tall, athletic, greying. Suit with no tie kind of guy, but always a flashy pocket square. On fridays and weekends he wears his golf attire. Think Richard Greenwood, (Workin’ Moms)

***About Character:**** *Former real estate agent, but has been the Ward 5 City Councillor 15 years running. Bill is considered a “Greybeard” or municipal government. He’s been at it for a long time and knows all the ins and outs. He’s incredibly popular, not just because of his extreme charisma, but also his moral flexibility when it comes allowing a “healthy dose” of political corruption. He likes ambitious people that know what they want, and won’t let moral or legal guidelines stifle their vision. He saw a lot of potential in Hannah when she started as his assistant. When Hannah hit her rock bottom, it was his idea to give her a leave of absence, as he felt a sense of responsibility for her. He’s given Hannah six months to show what she’s made of. If it works, he looks like a genius. If she fails, it’s not much money, his conscience is clear and in the meantime he can use the Task Force to his own personal and financial benefit when the opportunity arises.

***CHARACTER****:  *Nick

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ***28

***Episode: ****2*

***Appearance: ***White, thin and kind of scrawny. Slim shady like. Oshawa generals jersey. Knock off designer hat and shoes. Chain. Energetic, passionate, feels his emotions and is confident in them, which can make him a prima donna. The fashion of J Roc, the delivery of Western U frat bro, and the sincerity of a “cool” youth pastor, 

***About Character:**** *After getting his Bachelors from Western, Nick gave up on higher education to pursue his dream of becoming a hip hop legend. He moved back in with his mom and  new husband, Bill Tuft, at his mansion. That was 5 years ago. When Bill learns that the Task Force is putting together a tourism music video, he sees this as an opportunity to include Nick in order to write off past studio personal expenses. Nick joins forces with Jam Easy in making a great song, and wins his step-dad’s respect of his art. 

***CHARACTER****:  *Gord “Conspiracy Guy” 

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ***39

***Episode: ****2,4*

***Appearance: ***White, grisled beard, weary eyes, military surplus gear, phone mounted on a chest rig. Husky, but strong with a surprising range of movement, like a former soldier who’s stopped training.

***About Character:**** *Gord is a conspiracy-minded “truth warrior” who proudly identifies as a sovereign citizen.  He spends his days moderating threads on Truth Social, and uploading videos of his “auditing” police and other government workers to his pro-freedom channel. He’s paranoid, he’s ready for a fight, but when you get down to it he’s very thin-skinned. He comes across the Oshawa Tourism Task Force filming different Oshawa landmarks, he confronts them for “invading his privacy” and casts paranoid suspicions about their true intent. When Ashley arrives with his ”spy drone”, Gord takes it as a moment of bittersweet triumph: the government really is after him, and his “truth warrior” life wasn’t wasted.

***CHARACTER****:  *Samuel McLaughlin Impersonator #1

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ***45

***Episode: ***3

***Appearance: ***Middle aged man who is neither physically matching nor dressed for the part of Samuel.

***About Character:**** *Samuel shows up to audition as an R.S. McLaughlin impersonator for the upcoming civic holiday, but quickly fails when he not only cannot remember his line - “Oshawa”, but is legally required to let the task force know he’s not allowed within a certain distance of any children at the celebration.  

***CHARACTER****:  *Samuel McLaughlin, R.S

***Role Type****: *OCP

***Presenting Gender: ***Man

***Age: ***45

***Episode: ***3

***Appearance: ***Teddy Roosevelt aesthetic. Neatly trimmed, but bushy moustache. Balding, broad shoulders, stern, sharp eyes. (Think the real Samuel McLaughlin)

***About Character:**** *Samuel shows up at the office to audition as an R.S. McLaughlin impersonator for the upcoming civic holiday, but he insists he is not an actor at all and seems to believe he’s the real Samuel McLaughlin. Once hired, Samuel lingers in the office and gradually assumes control of the task force by exploiting weaknesses in Hannah’s communication with her team.

items.text:
CASTING CALL – Independent Short Film 

We are casting for an upcoming student short film exploring obsession, ambition, and the dark side of the ballet world.

Production: Student film via The American University of Rome

Director: Maxine Sutton

Cinematographer: Georgia Blackson

Shooting Dates: December 12–19

ROLES

NATASHA (Lead)

Female, 18–28

Ballet-trained (advanced preferred)

Must convey vulnerability, intensity, and psychological depth

Strong acting, presence, and physical performance required

Slavic accent preferred.

Pay: 250€ flat rate for entire production

MILA & SASHA (Supporting)

Female, 18–25

No ballet or dance experience required

Physically expressive roles with strong emotional reactions

Pay: 100€ flat rate for entire production

SYNOPSIS

Natasha, a talented but tormented ballerina, navigates a high-stakes audition that tests the limits of her physical and psychological endurance. As she strives for perfection under the watchful eye of the enigmatic Rudolph, the line between reality and terror begins to blur, forcing her to confront the true cost of ambition.

TO APPLY

Please complete the audition form and send it, along with a headshot, to: maxineclairesutton@gmail.com

items.text:
Hello!
Your time is here, join Ember Souls today!!

After the success of our first film, auditions are now open for Part 2 in 'The Turned Anthology'. This film follows the day to day life of Tommy and friends, showing the spark that starts the formation of the Ember Souls.

Please contact us about auditioning as we are looking for:
1 - Male (Mid 20's)
2 - Male (Early 20's) 
1 - Female (Early 20's) 

The sex and age of the characters is not fixed and can be altered to fit the performer!

If you can return your audition to us by midnight on Friday 31st of October.

As this is a donation based non-profit project we are currently unable to offer any pay for your work, we can however offer an IMDB credit and a chance to work with other creatives from across the North East!

Any questions or concerns please contact us!
theturnedproject@gmail.com

CASTING CALL — FEMALE LEAD 🎬

Banbury, Oxfordshire | £250 for 2 days + travel considered

We’re casting for the final scenes of Failsafe, a psychological short film currently in production with a professional crew.

Directed by Rob Hutt — award-winning filmmaker of Time Spent (23 awards, 22 nominations, 8.8 IMDb rating). You can view Rob’s IMDb profile here:
👉 https://www.imdb.com/name/nm4254248/?ref_=ext_shr_lnk

This project is already generating festival momentum and will be featured in Pro Movie Maker Magazine.

ROLE:
 • Female, playing age 25–35
 • Character: A game designer whose reality begins to fracture, blurring with the world she created. Performance requires range: strength, vulnerability, psychological depth.

DETAILS:
 • £250 for 2 days filming.
 • Shoot will take place across one Saturday & Sunday, back-to-back.
 • Filming must be completed on one of the following weekends:
 • 11–12 October 2025
 • 18–19 October 2025
 • 25–26 October 2025
 • Location: Banbury, Oxfordshire. Reasonable travel costs considered.
 • Short film — to be submitted to national and international film festivals.
 • Professional set with full crew.
 • Self-tape auditions required.

📩 To apply / receive the self-tape brief:
https://www.starnow.com/casting/failsafe-3020838/female-games-designer-5368483/ or DM directly.

✨ This is a chance to be part of a powerful, festival-ready film with proven pedigree.

👋 Hey Filmmakers! Just wanted to let you know about us if you aren't yet familiar. Saturation helps producers, directors, and production teams in film, TV, commercials, documentaries, and music videos streamline every stage of production. Think budgeting, payments, actualization, and expense tracking - all in one collaborative cloud-based platform.

We have a demo on our website, and it's also free to join: https://saturation.io/join

items.text:
Film crews are using Photoshop IDs and hand over cash envelopes to get paid?

Saturation's co-founders Jens Jacob & Simon Tam break down why film production financial tools haven't evolved like Figma, Frame.io, and Airtable did for their industries and how they're building the solution. From 20+ years in tech at Microsoft, Yahoo & Splunk to revolutionizing how $2B+ in budgets get managed for productions. Trusted by over 8,000 producers.

Szukamy dzieci i rodziców do udziału w planie zdjęciowym 📸

 **Dzieci:**
* 2–3 miesiące
* 5/6 miesięcy 
* 9 miesięcy
* 18 miesięcy (x2)

👨‍👩‍👧 **Szukamy także pary rodziców** (prawdziwi rodzice mile widziani, ale nie wymagane)

.

📅 **Termin:** II połowa października
🕒 **Czas trwania planu:** ok. 3–4 h
💰 **Stawka:** 300 PLN / osoba
💵 **Płatne od razu po planie**
📍 **Miejsce:** Warszawa

Zgłoszenia prosimy wysyłać na 📩 **monika@takamastudio.com**
W treści maila podaj:
* Imię dziecka
* Wiek dziecka + rozmiar ubrania
* Aktualne zdjęcie 

Z wybranymi osobami skontaktujemy się bezpośrednio.

📽️Projekt: Krótki, lekko surrealistyczny film, czarno - biały o aniele w połączeniu że stylem inspirowanym filmografią Wima Wendersa oraz Krzysztofa Kieślowskiego 

📅Data: jeden weekend w październiku, szczegóły do ustalenia 

📍Lokacja: Kraków oraz Skawina

💰Zapłata: 400 zł za dzień (łącznie 800 zł) + koszty za podróż 

Kogo szukamy:

Szukamy młodej (20-30 lat) jasnowłosej dziewczyny pełnej pozytywnej energii i charyzmy.  Otwartej na świat i lubiącej pracować z ludźmi

Wymagania:

- nauczenie się scenariusza

- brak widocznych tatuaży

Co odesłać 

- wizytówkę aktorską

- zdjęcia ( 1 full-body oraz 1 close-up) i/lub profil na social mediach

Zgłoszenia:

Proszę o odesłanie materiałów na maila: ignacyfialek@gmail.com 

Deadline: 3 października

items.text:
**SØGER STATIST / SKUESPILLER**

Vi arbejder på et lille, selvstændigt projekt, og vi søger en ekstra/skuespiller til hovedrollen. Idéen er at holde produktionen meget minimalistisk, uden budget, og færdiggøre den på blot en eller to dage, med fuldt fokus på kreativitet og spontanitet. Udstyr og crew vil også være meget begrænset. Konceptet for projektet er idéen omkring ***INSOMNIA - too tired to live too awake to dream.***

Vi søger en mand eller kvinde på 50–60 år.

📍 Lokation: Østerbro / Ryparken / Nordvest
🗓 Dato: 11. og 12. oktober
⏰ Tidsforbrug: Kun to dages optagelse – ca. 4 timer hver dag.

Hvis du har lyst til at være med, så send en kort besked med billede og lidt info om dig selv på elisahorcajada@gmail.com. 

Tak :)

items.groupTitle: hele landet / gratis casting for skuespillere og statister
items.summary:
**SØGER STATIST / SKUESPILLER**

Vi arbejder på et lille, selvstændigt projekt, og vi søger en ekstra/skuespiller til hovedrollen. Idéen er at holde produktionen meget minimalistisk, uden budget, og færdiggøre den på blot en eller to dage, med fuldt fokus på kreativitet og spontanitet. Udstyr og crew vil også være meget begrænset. Konceptet for projektet er idéen omkring ***INSOMNIA - too tired to live too awake to dream.***

Vi søger en mand eller kvinde på 50–60 år.

📍 Lokation: Østerbro / Ryparken / Nordvest
🗓 Dato: 11. og 12. oktober
⏰ Tidsforbrug: Kun to dages optagelse – ca. 4 timer hver dag.

Hvis du har lyst til at være med, så send en kort besked med billede og lidt info om dig selv på elisahorcajada@gmail.com. 

Tak :)

items.title: **SØGER STATIST / SKUESPILLER**

items.text:
Casting call!!! Jobbet er dsv ULØNNET

Her på Talentskolen I Næstved  er vi lige gået i gang med vores første øvelse for i år hvor vi skal filme og producere en meget lille kortfilm på ca 2 min og har derfor brug for en nogle dejlige skuespillere.

Det er en dags optagelse her næste måned (søndag d. 1 Nov.)

Filmning vil foregå i Næstved, og transport og forplejning står vi for, så ikke være bange for at skrive.

Der vil være øvelser nogle uger før filming så man ikke bare møder op og får et manus i hånden. 

**Vi søger 3 skuespiller 2 mænd og 1 dame **

mændene må godt være i spille alderen (26-35)

og en kvindelig skuespiller i spille alderen (50+)

Hvis i er interesseret skal i bare skrive til mig privat på facebook så svar jeg så hurtigt som muligt 
og hvis i kender nogle der måske kunne være interesseret så skal i bare tagge dem i kommentaren

**Logline:**
To venner forbereder sig på en vigtig aften, men bliver gentagne gange forstyrret af hverdagens små trivialiteter, cigaretter, lasagne og en mor, der bare vil være hjælpsom.

**Filmes genre:** Sort komedie

* **William (28 ish)**

William er en kontrollerende og lettere anspændt type, der forsøger at tage ansvar og holde styr på situationen – uanset hvor kaotisk eller banal den er. Han er tydeligt frustreret over sin mors konstante afbrydelser og Theodors manglende fokus. Under overfladen ligger et behov for at bevise sig selv – måske over for verden, måske over for sig selv.

* **Theoder (28 ish)**

Theodor er afslappet og lidt fjern, en drømmer med et tørt glimt i øjet. Han tager ikke situationen nær så seriøst som William og reagerer på kaos med humor eller passivitet. Han er loyal, men lidt af en wildcard – det er aldrig helt til at sige, om han er genial eller bare helt væk. Hans måde at "leve sig ind i rollen" viser både legesyge og en snert af noget mørkere.

* **Williams mor**

En klassisk overbeskyttende og påtrængende mor, der tydeligvis ikke forstår grænser – men heller ikke mener noget ondt med det. Hun træder ind i scenen med lasagne og strømpebukser og underminerer al "alvor" med hver sætning. Hendes komiske timing og totale mangel på situations fornemmelse fungerer som en ufrivillig sabotør af sønnens hemmelige planer.

Håber at høre fra jer snart 

Mvh.
Andrim, Lisa, Alexander, Lukas og Lukas

Hun træder ind i scenen med lasagne og strømpebukser og underminerer al "alvor" med hver sætning. Hendes komiske timing og totale mangel på situations fornemmelse fungerer som en ufrivillig sabotør af sønnens hemmelige planer.

Håber at høre fra jer snart 

Mvh.
Andrim, Lisa, Alexander, Lukas og Lukas

**SØGER 2 BØRN TIL KORTFILM I MORGEN (KØBENHAVNS FILM- OG FOTOSKOLE)**

Vi leder efter **2 børn i alderen 6–13 år** til en kortfilmsoptagelse (midtvejsfilm på overbygningen ved Københavns Film- og Fotoskole).

**Optagelserne er i morgen aften, fredag d. 3. oktober**, i området **Odsherred/Holbæk/Nordvestsjælland**.

Børnene skal spille en lille, men central scene som udklædte halloween-børn, der banker på døren til en stor herregård – en klassisk “slik eller ballade”-situation. Det er en sjov og overskuelig rolle, og en fin chance for at opleve en professionel filmproduktion på tæt hold.

**Praktisk:**
* Alder: 6–13 år
* Område: Odsherred / Holbæk / Nordvestsjælland
* Tidspunkt: Fredag d. 3. oktober (aften)
* Vi sørger for forplejning, og evt. udgifter dækkes.

Hvis du kender nogen, der kunne være interesseret, så skriv gerne til mig på mailen: [nogetfornogenfilm@gmail.com](mailto:nogetfornogenfilm@gmail.com) eller direkte til mit tel. nr.: 53706079.

items.text:
Rainhill Garrick Society are performing ‘ Habeus Corpus’ by Alan Bennett on February 12th-14th 2026.

Alan Bennett’s Habeus Corpus is set some time in the Seventies and follows the lives of the Wicksteed family. The story follows Dr and Muriel Wicksteed as they both seek pleasure and fun outside of their marital relationship. The farcical play is very fast paced, incredibly funny and occasionally surreal. The bumbling sex-obsessed British characters such as the virginal vicar, the ﬂat chested spinster, the peering doctor, his frustrated wife and of course a bra salesman man all come together in this bizarre and thoroughly entertaining story.

Parts available:-

Dennis Wicksteed - the hypochondriac son of Dr Wickseed, (20-30)

Felicity Rumpers - young, nubile, upper class  (20-30)

Constance Wicksteed - the sister of Dr Wicksteed, flat chested and sex starved, (20+) 

Play read through Tuesday 21st October at 7.30 in Rainhill Village Hall
Auditions- Thursday 23rd October at 7.30 Rainhill Village Hall 
Rehearsals are on Tuesdays and Thursday evenings 7.30-9.30 and the 3 Sundays prior to the performance.
Audition pieces are available on request. 

We are an amateur group so the roles are unpaid, but we are a well respected group of 83 years standing who enjoy great support from a large dedicated audience. 
The play is great fun with some slapstick and music but with some poignant moments that say a lot about relationships.

For further information, contact: sophiebrogan99@gmail.com

**Casting for: Korean Kpop Idol types, early 20's.**

Holding open auditions for several projects we are working on, looking for actors and actresses who can play  Korean Kpop singers and idols. This is not a music project, this is a short film/webseries project, thus looking for acting talent.

Asian ethnicity, early 20's look, attractive, in shape. You do not need to be Korean and you do not need to know how to sing (but if you can, that is a bonus). Non-union. Paid (TBD).

Auditions are Friday, Saturday, Sunday, October 10th, 11th, 12th in East Vancouver studio. You will perform a short set of sides and then do a monologue of your choice.

Shooting will be in Winter 2026.

If interested, please email castingproject604@gmail.comNOSPAM (remove 'NOSPAM') with your photos, resume with a cover letter about your experience or any training you have had and your availability for the three dates.

Shortlisted talent will be asked to audition.

Thank you for your attention.

PANOWIE (25-45) !!!
Do ról policjantów i gangsterów poszukujemy wysportowanych, dobrze zbudowanych mężczyzn w wieku 25-45 lat, mile widziane TATUAŻE.

Jeżeli marzysz o roli w serialu kryminalnym, wystarczy wypełnić formularz zgłoszeniowy dostępny na naszej stronie: http://www.outsetfilms.pl/casting01

Czekamy na Wasze zgłoszenia.
✨ Panie również mile widziane – mamy role dla każdego!

items.text:
CASTING CALL 

Self Tapes Wanted for University of Colorado Denver Senior Thesis Project

In-Person Callbacks in early October

TITLE: *Action! 1987*

PROJECT TYPE: Short Film (Student, Non-Union)

LOCATION: Denver Metro Area

TIMEFRAME: 2 Days of Shooting in late October 

SYNOPSIS: In 1987, a young woman, Luda, leaves a movie theatre with her cinephile boyfriend Julian. They argue about the morality of the action heroes they see on screen. Luda says the so-called “good guys” are always doing bad things. Julian thinks it’s more complicated than that.

The next day at work while helping with a children’s beauty pageant, Luda finds that right and wrong aren’t always so black and white when the parents of a young girl, Angie, leaves her alone in front of Luda. That night Luda and Julian walk into the movie theatre and she is shocked to see herself up on the silver screen.

COMPENSATION (Non-Union) : Reel, Food, Gas, Undying Appreciation

ROLE: 

Dad (Male, Late 30’s - Late 40’s): An stern and demanding pageant Dad with a wandering eye.

Please send your headshot/resume/other materials to [MARLEY.TREMMEL@UCDENVER.EDU](mailto:MARLEY.TREMMEL@UCDENVER.EDU) to receive sides and further instructions for submitting a self-tape. Thank you!

**UKRYTA PRAWDA  - WARSZAWA (22-24.10)**

Poszukuję epizodystów do ról:
1. **DOMINIKA  (24-30 lat)** -  bardzo atrakcyjna, zadbana. Zakochana w swoim mężu*. 22-24.10 Stawka 1800 zł KONIECZNE DOŚWIADCZENIE/DEMO*
2. **GRZEGORZ (35-43 lat)*** - * szemrany gość, wygląd może zdradzać, że jest gangsterem, prowadzi nielegalne interesy. Stawka 1000 zł, 2 dni

items.text:
Ich bin vielleicht nicht der geborene Top-Schauspieler oder das nächste Supermodel für die Kamera – in der Werbekommunikation überlasse ich das Rampenlicht gerne anderen. ABER ich habe etwas Großes im Sinn und bin bereit, einen neuen Weg zu gehen: Ich möchte das Medienhaus Mond Jung eröffnen! 🌙🌟

​Dieses Medienhaus ist keine spontane Idee; ich habe es über längere Zeit entwickelt, und es verfügt bereits über einige hauseigene Marken. Doch jetzt bin ich an einem spannenden und entscheidenden Punkt angekommen.  

Die Zeit der reinen Werbemittel-Produktion ist vorbei. Um die Vision von Mond Jung vollständig zu verwirklichen, muss ich Maschinen anschaffen, um haptische Ware (also physische Produkte!) produzieren zu können. 📦⚙️ 

​Um diesen nächsten Schritt zu machen und Mond Jung richtig voranzubringen, suche ich Unterstützung!

​Besonders an euch aus der Schauspiel- und Kreativszene gerichtet: Ich suche dringend Leute, die sich mit dem Medienhaus Mond Jung identifizieren und es als Vertreter (oder Promotor) auf die nächste Ebene heben möchten.  

Eure Präsenz und euer Netzwerk sind Gold wert, um unsere Marken bekannt zu machen! 🤝

​Wer hat Lust, Teil dieser spannenden Reise zu sein und Mond Jung mit aufzubauen? Schreibt mir eine DM, lasst uns connecten und dieses Ding zum Fliegen bringen! 💌

​#MondJung #Medienhaus #NeuesProjekt #Startup #Kreativszene #SchauspielerGesucht #Unterstützung #Vision

**Statistinnen gesucht für Kinodokumentarfilm**

Für einen szenischen Kinodokumentarfilm zum Thema „Liebe im Alter“ (Koproduktion mit dem ZDF) suchen wir kurzfristig Statistinnen.
Der Dreh findet morgen, Freitag 25.09., zwischen 16:00 und 18:00 Uhr im Museum in Bonn statt.

Bitte beachten Sie, dass lediglich eine kleine Aufwandsentschädigung (20 € die Stunde) gezahlt werden kann.

Wir freuen uns über Ihr Interesse und eine kurze Rückmeldung.

Hier unsere Website zu der Produktion:
[https://solange-es-nicht-aufhoert.de/](https://solange-es-nicht-aufhoert.de/)

Tickets are now available for our upcoming Actors and Filmmakers Networking Event, taking place on Sunday, October 26th.

 

Networking is essential for advancing your career in the industry, and Marble Academy has proudly facilitated these events for years. With over 90 attendees, our June gathering was a tremendous success, and we are determined to build on that momentum.

 

You will have the opportunity to connect with accomplished actors, visionary directors, prominent producers, and skilled crew members who can offer valuable insights and spark meaningful collaborations.

 

Think about it, if there were an event where you could connect with exceptionally talented cast and crew who could help bring your next project to life, wouldn’t you want to be there?

 

So, join us on Sunday, October 26th, from 2 PM to 6:30 PM at HOME Mcr, located at 2 Tony Wilson Place, Manchester, M15 4FN.

 

Secure your tickets through this link:

https://www.eventbrite.co.uk/e/actors-and-filmmakers-networking-event-tickets-1509159349239 

 

I look forward to seeing you there!

🌟 Get Ready to Ignite Your Acting Passion with Our Exciting Workshop! 🌟

 

Our last Self-Tape Workshop filled up quickly, leaving many interested individuals unable to attend, but don’t worry, we're excited to announce that another chance is just around the corner!

 

Join us at Marble Academy in Swinton, Manchester, on Monday, December 1st

 

You'll acquire practical insights and techniques that'll enhance your performance in auditions, boost your confidence on camera and create standout self-tapes!

 

**Spaces are VERY Limited!**

 

𝐁𝐨𝐨𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐰𝐨𝐫𝐤𝐬𝐡𝐨𝐩 𝐰𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐨𝐩𝐞𝐧 𝐨𝐧 𝐌𝐨𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐲, 𝟐𝟕𝐭𝐡 𝐎𝐜𝐭𝐨𝐛𝐞𝐫.

 

To claim your spot, email us at marbleacademy@hotmail.com with ‘SELF-TAPE WORKSHOP’ in the subject line.

𝐏𝐥𝐞𝐚𝐬𝐞 𝐞𝐧𝐬𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐞𝐫𝐯𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐢𝐬 𝐬𝐮𝐛𝐦𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐝 𝐛𝐲 𝐅𝐫𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐲, 𝐍𝐨𝐯𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟏𝟒𝐭𝐡.

 

Upon confirming your participation, you will receive a brief two-person scene to learn, along with a character description for the role you will portray (please include your age so I can send you age-appropriate sides).

These materials will be accompanied by the workshop address and additional details, which will be sent to you via email.

 

We look forward to seeing you there.

PIGE MED PROTESE SØGES TIL KORTFILM - (LØNNET) -ÅRHUS

Til kortfilmen “Dukkebarn” søger vi en pige med en ben protese eller arm protese til rollen som AURA. 

Lidt om filmen: 
“Dukkebarn udforsker den skrøbelige grænse mellem fantasi og virkelighed gennem øjnene på Aura. Hendes fascination til dukker bliver en måde at bearbejde hendes egen smertelige virkelighed og hendes forhold til sin krop. Gennem leg, skabelse og destruktion konfronteres hun med sine dybeste frugter og længsler. 

Alder: I mellem 6-12 år. 

Vi filmer i Århus d. 16-18 Januar 2026. Jobbet vil være lønnet, samt forplejning og transport. Søg gerne lige meget hvor i landet du bor. Vi ser gerne så mange som muligt;) 

Skriv til @Rirh.prod@gmail.com med emnet “CASTING -DUKKEBARN”. Skrive gerne lidt om dig selv, samt er billede og evt erfaring. 

Hvis du er gået videre til casting, eller fået rollen vil du få svar inden 10 Januar. 

Jeg glæder mig til at høre fra jer. 

Mvh Rebecca Renner Hansen - Dukkebarn film

Hendes fascination dukker made bearbejde sin egen smertefulde virkelighed hendes forhold krop. Gennem eg, skabelse og destruktion konfronteres hun med sine dybeste frygter og laengsler.'

items.text:
**CASTING CALL**

Til den ambitiøse og absurd-komiske kortfilm FLYT DIG, leder vi lige nu efter en række skuespillere. 

**LOGLINE**

En konfliktsky ung mand bliver udnyttet af sine venner og ignoreret af sin familie. Da hans rebelske fætter hjælper ham med at flytte, må han indse, at frihed ikke bare handler om at bryde ud – men om at turde definere sine egne grænser.

**ADAM **(hovedrolle, omkring 18)
* Ung af udseende
* Stille, meget almindelig, ikke særlig bemærkelsesværdig
* har svært ved at sætte grænser

**FAMILIEMEDLEM 1**

**FAMILIE MEDLEM 2**

**FAMILIEMEDLEM 3**

**FAMILIE MEDLEM 4**
* BIROLLER, ALLE mellem 40-80 år
* ALLE familiemedlemmer har replikker
* KØN/UDSEENDE er underordnet 

**ROOMIE 1**

**ROOMIE 2**

**ROOMIE 3**
* BIROLLER, DRENGE mellem 17-22
* ALLE roomies har replikker 
* UDSEENDE er underordnet

Optagelserne kommer til at ligge i Aarhus, omkring datoerne 14-15-16 oktober. Da dette er i samarbejde med Potemkin, Den Jyske Filmskole, er rollerne ulønnet.

Hvis man er interesseret i en/flere af rollerne, bedes man sende en mail på sara774g@gmail.som med alder og eventuel erfaring/showreel.

Vi glæder os til at høre fra jer!

Vh 

Sara Riahi, Freya Carlsen & Sylvester Byder

items.text:
We are now casting for our Halloween Party show .

The show will tour into community based venues, Nursing and Residential Homes, Day Centres.

We are seeking self-contained experienced hardworking singer/ performers who are keen to take quality musical shows to the community.

The Dates

Rehearsals –17th and 18th October in London

Playing Dates-20th -31st October-

We work Monday to Friday only.

The show is a one man/woman show so we are looking for experienced engaging performers with great singing voices,

We are looking for drivers with cars only

Please confirm where you are based in your application.

We offer £700 per week plus fuel on the road .

We are also casting our one man / woman musical show Winter Wonderland that will tour care homes and community based throughout December.

The show is production style show based on songs from the musicals Mary Poppins, White Christmas, Singing In The Rain, The Wizard Of Oz As well as traditional Christmas songs and carols, comedy routines and festive entertainment for all.

Dates

Rehearsals 24th -28th November

Playing dates 1st-23rd December

We perform two 60 minute shows 6 days a week.

We are offering 600 .00 per week fuel on the road and accommodation allowance when required.

MUST BE A DRIVER WITH A CAR

Please email details including a singing reel to

info@theentertainmentproviders.co.uk

CASTING CALL FOR PLAY IN LONDON:

I'm casting four roles (3 female/ 1 male) for a showcase reading of my new play 'The Beat of the Bronzewing' at the Hen & Chickens Theatre in Islington, London on November 12th. 

The Beat of the Bronzewing was longlisted for the Theatre 503 International Playwriting Award 2025 and focuses on three women in remote tropical Australia, desperate to turn their lives around yet paralysed by fear. It explores how their insecurities and the wild landscape magnify their loneliness and isolation, setting them on a course of self-destruction as they increasingly turn on each other. 

Apply via the Google Form link here: ([https://t.co/d98EEgkgK0](https://t.co/d98EEgkgK0?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR5Hu3UGD1qZxdMIWR2d_80GBkptrNYjvmQKWCmydP--a9Hs-hLLyq9GDFqZlA_aem_Tn4v_Jq0QGNGHkakZGOTFw)). 

Know someone who might be interested? Please spread the word!

 

Important info:  

| Rehearsals on November 9th (10am-6pm) and November 12th (2:30-7pm)

| In-person auditions on October 8th (12-5pm) at the Old Red Lion Theatre in Angel, Islington following a selection (let us know if you need an alternative) 

| Volunteer opportunity - all actors will be given £50 pounds for expenses

| Apply via Google Form link here: ([https://t.co/d98EEgkgK0](https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fd98EEgkgK0%3Ffbclid%3DIwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR6STL3lXt8cdBCGpSYrv5XvpSHW_IA3JoKT1r83vfoq93QMm80Vsj_31_s09Q_aem_cSh3Con8n2nt4AWPGVxuRQ&h=AT3UxWehtfMsSwB5REWXCX3UHOR-IbCtMgXw11AVLk6tzDWjrVusQvMal4tBpcgnFYk6zyQaOjGLupowpQG2C_2Lnir-BGUKBI9MH_CMk-pF1FA-OIIZsoxFFo2bSplp5WYnUXM019O0AA&__tn__=-UK-R&c[0]=AT3ZSFem3LQLGHpnYQQix_aB1OTC-II_z6ULdAtsi-abLh1hVZ6JVCHBA2u98UrsMqLeuH-VMmJqsPkp102wldtR3ternY9MXCYToG6v5AsMe_3MJvv4-JL2oxzyNfi1_K7uf8f1E10-EvfRY4j_OFAP6nnjb1-iHjbe3u5HTKwR)) - thank you!

sharedPost.text:
MOVIETIME KW 40/2025

Ein Serienklassiker verabschiedet sich, Remake eines Kinderbuchklassikers und Kinofeeling für die Swifties

Die aktuelle Kalenderwoche hat es in sich, zunächst das Grande Finale von DOWNTOWN ABBEY (Stadtkino Horn) sowie fast 40 Jahre danach die Neuverfilmung von Michael Endes MOMO (Babylon Kino Horn,  Stadtkinocenter Laa und Filmbühne Waidhofen).

Ende September startete das Langfilmdebüt von Marie Luise Lehner in den Lichtspielhäusern. Das Ergebnis unseres Gespräches hören Sie in der Sendung.

Musikalisch gedenken wir der kürzlich verstorbenen Claudia Cardinale. 

Sarah Fuchs führt sie durch das nun wöchentliche Filmmagazin und sagt Ihnen auch, für welchen Film sich der Kinobesuch lohnt.

Mittwoch 01.10.2025 von 18 - 19 h auf radioYpsilon 94.5 oder via Stream (http://mp3.radioypsilon.at:8000/)

We are seeking enthusiastic actresses for an upcoming independent zombie movie. This project blends horror, suspense, and dark humor. Shooting dates are TBD and will take place in the local area.

Who we are looking for? 

Women aged 16-28 who have a passion for horror! We have leading roles that need to be filled and want young up and coming talent to take that spotlight! 

WE ARE SEARCHING FOR TONS OF NEW TALENT AND ENCOURAGE ALL WOMAN OF ALL BACKGROUNDS TO APPLY. WE DEDICATE OUR PROCESS INTO INVOLVING AND UPLIFITING THOSE WHO MAY FACE BARRIERS. (If you need accommodations please let us know)

To be considered, please leave your contact info in the link below and our team will be in contact shortly.

CASTING CALL for a SHORT we are producing in November.

COLD FEET

A dark comedy --- On his wedding day, Thomas tries to weasel his way out of lifetime commitment. But the universe has other plans for him.

Casting for

Thomas - The groom. A go-with-the-flow guy who realises too late that getting married is not what he wants.

Elliott - The best man who tries to set his friend on the right path.

Jane - An intense bride, who refuses to see the ugly truth about the supposed love of her life.

Must be willing to travel to Beaconsfield, Buckinghamshire (HP9).

Filming dates tentatively set for November 29-30, 2025.

This is a paid opportunity. Short film rates.

Please fill out this form to register your interest! https://forms.gle/U8PgSfkotmqSa9M16

Casting Call – Fitness Model & Child Model for E-Bike Commercial Shoot

We are looking for two roles for our upcoming commercial shoot for an electric bike brand:

1. Adult Model

📍 Location: Los Angeles
📅 Date: Friday, October 4th
🕓 Time: 4:00 PM – 7:00 PM
💰 Compensation: $50/hour

Requirements:
 • Male or female, athletic / fit body type
 • Comfortable posing for lifestyle & product photography

2. Child Model

📍 Location: Los Angeles
📅 Date: Friday, October 4th
🕓 Time: 4:00 PM – 7:00 PM
💰 Compensation: $50/hour

Requirements:
 • Boy, age 8–13
 • Comfortable in front of the camera
 • Parent/guardian must accompany during shoot

⸻

Details:
 • Paid opportunity ($50/hour)
 • Photos will be used for brand advertising and online media

If interested, please send me a direct message with:
✔️ Recent photos or portfolio
✔️ Age (for child applicants)
✔️ Contact info (email/phone)

👉 Please DM only.

items.text:
**🎬 CASTING DO TELEDYSKU – PŁATNE 🎬**

**Warszawa**

Poszukujemy osób z doświadczeniem aktorskim lub modelingowym do udziału w teledysku młodego i bardzo utalentowanego wykonawcy. Projekt ma charakter surrealistyczny i konceptualny.

📅** Termin realizacji: 05.10 (niedziela), godz. 14:00 – ok. 02:00** (część nocy)

💰 **Projekt płatny**

👉** Poszukiwane role:**

**1. Dziadek** – mężczyzna w wieku 50–75 lat

**2. Mężczyzna** – w wieku 30–45 lat

📩 Zgłoszenia prosimy przesyłać na adres: **casting.kamilaboichenko@gmail.com**

W tytule maila należy wpisać: **ROLA – TELEDYSK – Imię i Nazwisko**

**Do zgłoszenia należy dołączyć:**

1. Imię i nazwisko + wiek

2. Miasto zamieszkania

3. Aktualne zdjęcia (portret + sylwetka)

4. Informację o doświadczeniu + wizytówkę lub showreel (jeśli jest)

5. Wymiary, rozmiar ubrań i butów

6. Dane kontaktowe: nr telefonu i adres e-mail

Zapraszam do udziału w wyjątkowym projekcie – czekamy na Wasze zgłoszenia!

Pozdrawiam serdecznie,

Reżyserka castingu 

Kamila Boichenko

sharedPost.text:
🎭🎶 CASTINGI DO MUSICALU „S!X” WE WROCŁAWSKIM TEATRZE DIALOGU! 🎶🎭

Już w kwietniu 2026 roku odbędzie się trzecia polska premiera światowego hitu – musicalu „S!X” autorstwa Toby’ego Marlowa i Lucy Moss, w reżyserii Michała Jagodzińskiego. 🔥

👉 Poszukujemy:
✨ Aktorek musicalowych – pełnoletnich, mieszkających na Dolnym Śląsku, studentek i absolwentek szkół aktorskich oraz muzycznych, związanych ze sceną musicalową.
✨ Gitarzystki i basistki – instrumentalistek z doświadczeniem scenicznym, najlepiej z obszaru muzyki teatralnej lub koncertowej.

📅 Terminy:
Aktorki musicalowe – casting wieloetapowy: zgłoszenia do 12 października 2025, godz. 23:59.
Gitarzystka i basistka –  wyłącznie jeden etap: zgłoszenia również do 12 października 2025, godz. 23:59.

📩 Zgłoszenia przyjmujemy mailowo na adres: six@teatr-dialogu.pl

W tytule maila: „Imię i nazwisko – Postać/Instrument – SIX”.

Szczegóły, wymagania oraz zakresy wokalne znajdziecie w pełnych ogłoszeniach ➡️ teatr-dialogu.pl/castingi/

Dołącz do zespołu, który stworzy trzecią polską premierę tego wyjątkowego musicalu! 💜👑🎤

items.text:
CASTING CALL - FEATURE FILM 

Please, do NOT email if you do not fit the brief!

Shooting Location: The Netherlands
Bruce male | 30 – 45 | English: native 
Black, African American or Caribbean

Requirements:
Based in Europe (EU passport)
Native speaker of American English
Age range: 30–45 years old

European based American-English speaking actor for the role of BRUCE in the Dutch Comedy Film.

We are looking for an actor to play the role of young and ambitious American movie director Bruce in the upcoming Dutch comedy film.

The film is based on the best-selling novel Wen Er Maar Aan, written by Dutch actress and author Maike Meijer.

Shooting date: December 3th 2025 in the Netherlands 
Travel day: December 2th 2025 (Travel day back on the same day as the shooting day or the morning after)

Fee:
€4.000 all-in (shooting day + travel day(s))
Overnight stay will be covered by the production
Travel expenses will be covered by the production

If you are selected to record a self-tape, you will receive further details via email.

>> ancagency_submissions@hotmail.com 

@followers @top fans

**GotFat Productions søger baggrundstatister til forskellige roller i en kortfilm, som skal skydes i uge 41 i Aarhus V (Gellerup):**

Vi søger blandt andet:
* statister til at stå i baggrunden i et supermarked
* statister til at være i baggrunden af et værtshus
* statister til at være i baggrunden af en gågade
* børn af anden etnisk herkomst (både drenge og piger)

Praktisk info:
* Jobbet er ulønnet, men vi står for forfriskninger og en fed oplevelse!
* Optagedagene varierer alt efter hvilken statistrolle, det drejer sig om.

**Alt har interesse, så tøv ikke med at send en mail på: vivi@gotfat.dk**

items.text:
Please get the Word Out that Jodi Purdy is looking for 3 Generations from Rhode Island - Grampa, his Son and his Grandson for a Commercial for a Medical Company.  

This pays $500 per person for one day on set with a professional crew and award-winning Director.

I just cast 16 actors in one of my clients Commercials in Austin Texas! Surely, I can find 3 in Rhode Island!

The boy has to live in Rhode Island.  So a boy between 6 and 9 and his dad would be great! I can find an actor to play the Grampa!!

Help a girl out and share if you live in RI!! 

I don’t want to have to go to RI!  

But I will, I’ll have a good Olde Fashion Casting Call! Remember those??

CASTING CALL - FEATURE FILM 

Please, do NOT email if you do not fit the brief!

Shooting Location: The Netherlands
Bruce male | 30 – 45 | English: native 
Black, African American or Caribbean

Requirements:
Based in Europe (EU passport)
Native speaker of American English
Age range: 30–45 years old

European based American-English speaking actor for the role of BRUCE in the Dutch Comedy Film.

We are looking for an actor to play the role of young and ambitious American movie director Bruce in the upcoming Dutch comedy film.

The film is based on the best-selling novel Wen Er Maar Aan, written by Dutch actress and author Maike Meijer.

Shooting date: December 3th 2025 in the Netherlands 
Travel day: December 2th 2025 (Travel day back on the same day as the shooting day or the morning after)

Fee:
€4.000 all-in (shooting day + travel day(s))
Overnight stay will be covered by the production
Travel expenses will be covered by the production

If you are selected to record a self-tape, you will receive further details via email.

>> ancagency_submissions@hotmail.com 

@followers @top fans
