**Actors wanted for Dick Whittington, Valley Theatre’s annual seasonal panto.**

**Audition date and time;**** 7.15pm, Monday 13****th**** October 2025, at Valley Theatre, Childwall Valley Rd, Liverpool L27 3YA**

**Performance dates:**** Sat  17****th**** Jan 2026(afternoon and eve) and Sun  18****th**** Jan 2026 (afternoon only);**

**Rehearsal days;**** Monday 7pm whole cast usually; Thursday eve selected scenes.**

Valley Theatre’s traditional panto has become legendary in the area. As a community theatre we pride ourselves on keeping the prices family friendly without compromising on the quality. We like to offer a  traditional storyline with well-loved panto routines, popular music, up-to-date and local references, strong on humour.

This is a great opportunity for actors wanting to gain unbeatable stage experience  with a friendly and supportive production team.

Wide range of parts available for the experienced and beginner alike. No prep needed for the audition.

Please note: this is non-paying.

More details [info@valleytheatre.co.uk](mailto:info@valleytheatre.co.uk)

Casting!

​[Gdańsk]

Szukam tancerki (tancerki/aktorki) do spektaklu Lilije; to mroczny i epicki spektakl dramatyczno-taneczny na podstawie ballady Mickiewicza z tańcem, grą na instrumentach i śpiewem wieloglosowym na żywo.

Tu zwiastun: [https://youtube.com/shorts/QoVYI9z-c0E?si=vL0OseuQpHg_DtLT](https://youtube.com/shorts/QoVYI9z-c0E?si=vL0OseuQpHg_DtLT)

Tu więcej informacji: [https://www.facebook.com/share/18bUFBgxwr/](https://www.facebook.com/share/18bUFBgxwr/)

Rola zasadniczo bez te​kstu; kilka linijek mówionych wspólnie ze wszystkimi. Umiejętność śpiewu, szczególnie na biało, będzie dużym atutem. Taniec współczesny, improwizacja, teatr tańca są wymagane.

Projekt non-profit, próby w październiku i listopadzie w poniedziałki od 19:30-21:30 w ACK UG. Spektakle płatne, w tym roku grania 7 i 14 grudnia. 

Premiera odbyła się w czerwcu, spektakl cieszył się dużym zainteresowaniem.

Zgłoszenie prześlij na [weronikakamola@gmail.com](mailto:weronikakamola@gmail.com), a w nim:

- ​zdjęcie, wzrost i wiek

- opis swojego doświadczenia tanecznego i śpiewaczego 

- filmik, na którym widać, jak tańczysz

items.text:
CASTING CALL/ NON-UNION 

Casting Russian speaking roles in the short anti-war film 'During Winter, I Thought of My Father' written and directed by Danill Vasilyev. 

Please submit resume, headshot(s), and demo reel (if applicable) to duringwinter26@gmail.com to receive sides. 

Audition submission deadline: OCTOBER 18, 2025

Character descriptions below: 

ARTYOM

Russian speaking man, early 20s.

Description: Having seen the horrors of war firsthand, this young man became a conscientious objector who deserted the war. And despite paying a high price for his decision, losing a leg to frostbite, Artyom remains entrenched in his anti-war beliefs. A bright young

man from a middle-class family, who loves poetry and shoemaking, Artyom uses every ounce of his physical and mental might to get back to his family. 

VLADIMIR 

Russian speaking man, 50s-60s. 

A staunch patriot who was once a soldier too. A decorated one, whose pride in his heroic exploits for the Motherland could be felt from afar. But now, the old man stands alone. No family, no friends, no backing from the state which he holds so dear. His only son died

in a war years ago. All that’s left is the inextinguishable belief in his national identity, which has been built from years of tradition and pride. 

Rate: Unpaid, travel and food will be provided.

**Casting for: East Asian actors, all types, all ages**

Holding open auditions for Asian actors, men and women, for a number of Asian film and episodic projects (action, thriller, drama, rom-com) we are working on.

East Asian ethnicity, looking for early 20's look (for group 1) and all ages (for group 2). Non-union. Payment status depends on the project.

Auditions are Friday, Saturday, Sunday, October 10th, 11th, 12th in East Vancouver studio. You will perform a short set of sides and then do a monologue of your choice.

Shooting will be throughout Fall and Winter 2025/2026.

If interested, please email castingproject604@gmail.comNOSPAM (remove 'NOSPAM') with your photos, resume with a cover letter about your experience or any training you have had and your availability for the three dates.

Shortlisted talent will be asked to audition.

Thank you for your attention.

- dwie kobiety o wyzywającym typie urody
- muszą być ekstremalnie podobne i tak samo wystylizowane 
- 30-45 lat
- kobiety o przerysowanym typie urody
- charakter przyciągający uwagę

Zdjęcia: 8.10 na terenie Warszawy lub w najbliższej okolicy.

Więcej szczegółów w wiadomości prywatnej.

** CASTING DO 3. SEZONU „BITWY O GOŚCI” (TVN) JESIEŃ/ZIMA 2025! **

Prowadzisz miejsce noclegowe w Polsce – pensjonat, agroturystykę, glamping, domek, apartament czy butikowy hotel?
Chcesz pokazać je milionom widzów TVN i sprawdzić, jak wypadniesz na tle innych gospodarzy? 

** 2. sezon programu bije rekordy oglądalności – teraz czas na Was i Wasze miejsce!**

Zgłoś się razem z drugą osobą – bo w tej przygodzie startują pary gospodarzy: rodzina, partnerzy, rodzeństwo, przyjaciele, znajomi 

**Jeśli chcesz uzyskać więcej informacji napisz do mnie wiadomość prywatną.**

 Nie czekaj – pokaż, czym wyróżnia się Wasz obiekt i weź udział w „Bitwie o Gości”!

COMMERCIAL CASTING CALL

Seeking background extras for a commercial film shoot! This is a full day shoot for Windstar Studios and our client. 

**Roles:** Background extras. NO speaking lines. 

**Shooting date**: Tuesday, October 7th, 2025. 

**Location: **Colorado Springs, CO (please reach out for more details)

**Timeframe:** 9am-6pm (approximately)

**Rate:** $250 for the day - lunch included

Talent will also need to bring wardrobe options representing the 4 seasons. 

Please shoot me an email at jensina@windstarstudios.com if you're interested or have any questions! No auditions necessary!

items.text:
CASTING CALL: Looking for a young girl, age 5-10, for a female-directed short film shooting this fall! 

Title: "The Garden"

Synopsis: When a child abandoned in youth faces abandonment again as an adult, they must learn to define themselves apart from those who left or lose their chance at love. 

Role: Young Ali, playing a younger version of the film's protagonist. This is actually a non-speaking role, but still very important to the film.

Compensation: Credit, meals, copy of footage for reel. Perfect for a kid looking to try acting or get more experience on a film set.

Parents, please Contact: thegardenvp@gmail.com with a headshot, and we'll send more info for a self-tape!

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of text that says 'The Garden Logline When a child abandoned in youth faces abandonment again as an adult, they must learn to define themselves apart from those who left or lose their chance at love. Production Info Drama set in both the real world and the fantastical world (virtual production) of The Garden. ·Format: 10-minute short film .Location: Denver & surrounding areas •Shoot Dates: October-November november 2025 Director's note So often what's within us is buried or forgotten. The Garden is where they uncover it it-and and learn to find resolution from ourselves.'

May be a graphic of 1 person and text that says 'Young Ai FEMALE | 5-10 A tender, hopeful child who longed for her parents' love, even as they turned away. Despite her efforts, she could never make them stay. minor Character non-Speaking Role'

items.text:
🎬 Girls wanted! – Sei Teil von „Josie“ 🎬✨

Du liebst Dreharbeiten, Sportwagen und gute Vibes? 🚗🔥 Dann haben wir genau das Richtige für dich!

Für unseren Film „Josie“ drehen wir im Stil vom „Fast & Furious“, einige exklusive Szenen in einer Luxus-Autowerkstatt mit Traumwagen in Solingen – und DU kannst dabei sein!

💃 Gesucht: Sympathische Damen, die Lust haben, locker & stylisch vor der Kamera mitzuwirken.(Party feeling)
🎥 Schauspiel-Erfahrung? Nicht nötig! Wichtig ist deine Ausstrahlung und Spaß am Mitmachen.
🥂 Dich erwartet: Ein einzigartiges Erlebnis, ein cooles Team und ganz viel Lifestyle-Feeling.
Drehort in Solingen 
Drehtermin noch offen, wird nach Absprache festgelegt

👉 Sei Teil des Films & melde dich jetzt!

Film Club NRW in Facebook wir sind eine No Profit Gruppe
Ansprechpartner: Hubert Balint

items.text:
**SØGES: 6 statister til julefrokost-optagelse i Ishøj (mandag d. 6. oktober kl. 13.00–13.30)**

Vi søger **6 statister** til en kort optagelse på **Industrigrenen 15, 2636 Ishøj** **mandag d. 6. oktober** kl. **13.00–13.30**.

**Opgaven:**
Du skal **ikke sige noget** – bare sidde ved et opdækket bord og “lege”, at du nyder en **hyggelig julefrokost**.

**Påklædning:**
Pænt tøj (ikke overdresset).

**Tak for hjælpen:**
Som tak får du **4 kuverter til Gaudiums Eksklusiv Særmenu (værdi 900 kr)**: gaudium.dk/produkt/eksklusiv-saermenu/

**Interesseret?**
Skriv en kort besked til **simon@gaudium.dk** med emnet *“Statist Ishøj”* og dit navn/telefonnummer.
Pladser tildeles løbende – først til mølle.

Tak! 🙌
/Simon, Gaudium.dk
